死んじゃいない お前とお前の連鎖
Not dead, you and your chain

59
00:05:05,548 --> 00:05:10,048
何時の世も 過去も未来も現在にあるんだ
In any era, the past and future are in the present

60
00:05:10,548 --> 00:05:13,248
生きていることを 愚直に果たせよ
Fulfill the act of living honestly

61
00:05:13,248 --> 00:05:15,548
目指せハッピーエンド
Aim for a happy ending

62
00:05:15,548 --> 00:05:16,848
アンデッド！
Undead!

63
00:05:16,848 --> 00:05:19,448
死んじゃいない お前に言っているんだ
Not dead, I'm telling you

64
00:05:19,448 --> 00:05:21,848
幸せを諦めてしまうな
Don't give up on happiness

65
00:05:22,048 --> 00:05:23,548
人で在れ
Be human

66
00:05:23,648 --> 00:05:26,548
ただ苦しみに慣れて 耐えているだけじゃ
Just getting used to pain and enduring it

67
00:05:26,548 --> 00:05:30,048
死んでいるも同然 屍のアンデッド
Is as good as dead, a corpse-like undead

68
00:05:30,348 --> 00:05:32,848
UNHAPPY? 悩める人の子よ
Unhappy? Children troubled

69
00:05:32,848 --> 00:05:35,348
UNLUCKY? 人成らざる者も
Unlucky? Those who don't become people

70
00:05:35,348 --> 00:05:37,848
BE HAPPY! 弛まず目指せよ
Be happy! Aim without slack

71
00:05:37,848 --> 00:05:40,448
アンデッド! 生きているんだろ
Undead! You're alive, right?

72
00:05:40,448 --> 00:05:43,048
不幸に浸るも 幸せになるのも
Whether you wallow in unhappiness or become happy

73
00:05:43,048 --> 00:05:45,548
そう全部全部お前だ
Yes, it's all, all you

74
00:05:45,548 --> 00:05:49,048
古今東西 一切合切 森羅万象 ピースピース
Throughout the ages, everything, all creation, peace peace

75
00:05:49,048 --> 00:05:51,548
Past and future / Can't change the past

76
00:05:51,548 --> 00:05:54,048
Past and future / Run for the future

77
00:05:54,048 --> 00:05:56,548
人の在る所に何時も憂い事
Wherever there are people, there is always sorrow

78
00:05:56,548 --> 00:05:59,048
生き抜けこの化物ばかりの物語
Survive this story full of monsters

79
00:06:15,048 --> 00:06:18,548
IRIS OUT
[Title: IRIS OUT]

80
00:06:29,048 --> 00:06:34,048
駄目駄目駄目 脳みその中から「やめろ馬鹿」と喚くモラリティ
Damn, damn, damn, a morality
that shouts "Quit it, idiot" from inside the brain

81
00:06:35,548 --> 00:06:36,548
ダーリンベイビーダーリン
Darling baby darling

82
00:06:36,548 --> 00:06:42,548
半端なくラブ！ときらめき浮き足立つフィロソフィ
I'm terribly in love! Philosophy
that makes me twinkle and float

83
00:06:43,048 --> 00:06:45,848
死ぬほど可愛い上目遣い
It's dying-ly cute, the way you look up

84
00:06:45,848 --> 00:06:48,348
なにがし法に触れるくらい
To the point of breaking some law

85
00:06:48,348 --> 00:06:50,848
ばら撒く乱心 気づけば蕩尽
Scattering insanity, before I know it, I'm squandering

86
