瞳孔バチ開いて溺れ死にそう
My pupils are blown wide open,
I feel like I'm drowning

93
00:07:16,048 --> 00:07:21,048
今この世で君だけ大正解
Right now, you are the only correct answer in this world

94
00:07:26,048 --> 00:07:28,548
ひっくり返っても勝ちようない
I can't win even if I flip over

95
00:07:28,548 --> 00:07:31,048
君だけルールは適用外
You are the only exception to the rules

96
00:07:31,048 --> 00:07:33,548
四つともオセロは黒しかない
Even in Othello, all four corners are only black

97
00:07:33,548 --> 00:07:36,048
カツアゲ放題
All-you-can-steal

98
00:07:36,048 --> 00:07:38,548
君が笑顔で放ったアバダケダブラ
Abada Kedavra you shot with a smile

99
00:07:38,548 --> 00:07:41,048
デコにスティグマ 申し訳ねえな
Stigma on your forehead, sorry about that

100
00:07:41,048 --> 00:07:43,548
矢を刺して 貫いて ここ弱点
I'll pierce it, run it through, this is the weak point

101
00:07:43,548 --> 00:07:46,048
死ぬほど可愛い上目遣い
It's dying-ly cute, the way you look up

102
00:07:46,048 --> 00:07:48,548
なにがし法に触れるくらい
To the point of breaking some law

103
00:07:48,548 --> 00:07:51,048
ばら撒く乱心 気づけば蕩尽
Scattering insanity, before I know it, I'm squandering

104
00:07:51,048 --> 00:07:53,548
この世に生まれた君が悪い
You, who were born into this world, are at fault

105
00:07:53,548 --> 00:07:56,048
パチモンでもいい何でもいい
A knock-off is fine, anything is fine

106
00:07:56,048 --> 00:07:58,548
今君と名付いてる全て欲しい
I want everything that is named "you" right now

107
00:07:58,548 --> 00:08:03,048
頸動脈からアイラブユーが噴き出て アイリスアウト
"I love you" sprays out from my carotid artery
Iris out

108
